comments: A truly inspiring and gifted teacher, Matt\'s best quality as a professor is his ability to pull the best work out of his students.

COOLEST TEACHER ON THE FACE OF THE PLANET! Truly an incredible visionary, such a helpful mentor with admirable qualities such as one does not see very much in professors these days. If only there could be more Matthew Tailfords in the world. Alas, he is an exellent uncle too.
